Class RegistrationNumber

  • java.lang.Object
    • Car.RegistrationNumber

  • public final class RegistrationNumber
extends java.lang.Object

    Car.RegistrationNumber

    This is a class designed to generate unique registration numbers for cars. A registration number consists of two components: 1 character followed by 4 numbers eg. "A1234".
